# Cooperative Brainstorming with Approach Evaluation

@prefix qp: <https://qualia.org/ontology/cooperative-projects#> .

# Idea with Approach & Debt Awareness
{ ?idea a qp:Idea ; qp:approachType ?app . } => { ?idea qp:genesisIdea ?idea . } .

# Link to Value-Complexity
{ ?idea qp:impactScore ?impact ; qp:complexityScore ?comp . } => { ?idea qp:valueComplexityQuadrant ?quad . } .